column2: "<%me>...? How... do you know my name? Why do you have Clarissa?"
"Haha... Unbelievable. To think I fell for such a stupid trick."
"I will grant you a swift end. Sleep peacefully."
"This reading... is Darker? Dark Falz!? No... something far more powerful!!"
"...do not stand in my way. She is to die here. She must die here!"
"Your face!? Your parameters!? I'm detecting evidence of time travel!"
"What is going on here!? Who or what is that Dark Falz!?"
